BM01 pressure sensor driver for Raspberry Pi

input voltage should be 5V, and the analog output is 0-4V

the digital output will be 1 when the pressure is greater than a threshold, and 0 when the pressure is less than the threshold.

Wiring:
GND -> GND
VCC -> 5V
DO -> GPIO 20

ros2 topic echo /pressure_detected

➜  Robonix git:(main) ✗ ros2 topic echo /pressure_detected
data: false
